modules.description: Provides functions to integrate QCheck 0.8 test runners with OUnit, merging custom and OUnit-specific execution logic. Works with test cases and test suites defined in QCheck and OUnit. Enables running QCheck tests within OUnit environments without manual configuration.

Provides test execution and reporting capabilities by running QCheck tests and integrating with OUnit. Supports command-line arguments for configuration and offers exit codes based on test success. Can execute multiple tests, handle verbose output, and interoperate with OUnit test frameworks. Example: run a suite of property-based tests and generate pass/fail reports.
